    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Well-kept good-condition vehicle that presents nicely overall and should make a solid, enjoyable driver. It runs and drives well, feels mechanically sound, and appears to have been maintained, with the kind of normal cosmetic wear and age-related imperfections you\u2019d expect from an honest used vehicle rather than a showpiece. A buyer can expect a clean, presentable car that is ready to be used and enjoyed.",
