    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels with potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little runabout with plenty of life left for the right buyer. Ideal as a budget commuter, first project, or spare car to keep you moving without spending a fortune. If you\u2019re practical and don\u2019t mind giving it a bit of TLC, there\u2019s good value here.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project car with strong enthusiast potential. The drivetrain feels eager, the chassis is fundamentally serviceable, and it has the kind of honest wear that makes it a great candidate for a budget build, parts runner, or hands-on daily revival. Not perfect cosmetically and it will want attention, but it presents as a complete, usable platform with plenty of life left for the right owner. Priced to move for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap ride. Rough but running. Gets you from A to B without draining your wallet. Priced to sell fast.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A car with stories in its steel and plenty of road still left for the right next chapter. This is the kind of find that speaks to someone who appreciates character over polish\u2014a practical, budget-friendly ride with an unmistakable presence and the kind of honest, well-worn charm that turns errands into little adventures. Whether you need inexpensive transportation, a hands-on project, or a dependable stand-in with personality, this one offers real potential at a price that leaves room to make it your own.",
      "price": 4800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Honest, affordable transportation with solid value for the price. This vehicle shows its age cosmetically and is best suited for a buyer looking for a practical, low-cost option, a second car, or a project with potential. Presented transparently and priced to move, it offers a straightforward way into vehicle ownership without stretching the budget.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car you can tinker with or use for parts? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest budget-friendly option with plenty of potential for the right buyer. A good fit for someone handy, a project seeker, or anyone needing a low-cost vehicle to work with. Priced to sell and ready to go to its next home.",
      "price": 4200.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Tough, inexpensive driver with solid bones and plenty of potential. Starts up, runs, and offers a straightforward mechanical setup that makes it a great budget commuter, shop truck, or weekend project. Shows its age cosmetically and will want attention in spots, but the core package is there: usable powertrain, practical cabin, and the kind of simple, serviceable platform enthusiasts appreciate. If you want an affordable vehicle you can drive now and improve over time, this one makes a compelling case.",
